>> My canonical small example of perfection in Solaris would be Jeff 
>> Bonwick's mod-by-a-billion code in hrt2ts():
>>
>> 
http://cvs.opensolaris.org/source/xref/onnv/onnv-gate/usr/src/uts/common/os/timers.c#875
 
